      "type": "conversation",
      "title": "Conversation Practice 1（会話）: The Commute",
      "context": "Talking about daily routines.",
      "lines": [
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "仕事は 何ですか。",
          "en": "What is your job?",
          "terms": [
            "v_shigoto",
            "v_nani"
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "会社員です。毎日 東京へ 行きます。",
          "en": "I am a company employee. I go to Tokyo every day.",
          "terms": [
            "v_kaishain",
            "v_mainichi",
            "v_iku"
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "朝は 早いですか。",
          "en": "Is the morning early?",
          "terms": [
            "k_asa",
            "v_hayai"
          ]
        },
        {
          "spk": "B",
          "jp": "はい。五時に 早起きします。",
          "en": "Yes. I wake up early at 5 o'clock.",
          "terms": [
            "v_hayaoki"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "conversation",
      "title": "Conversation Practice 2（会話）: At the Station",
      "context": "Asking about trains.",
      "lines": [
        {
          "spk": "A",
          "jp": "すみません。この 電車は 急行ですか。",
          "en": "Excuse me. Is this train an express?",
          "terms": [
            "v_densha",
            "v_kyuukou"
          ]
